msgctxt "384_Sodachi"
msgid "Here's to the new champion, Ehama-san! Congratulations!"
msgstr "¡Aquí está el nuevo campeón, Ehama-san! ¡Felicidades!"

msgctxt "396_Saejima"
msgid "Good job."
msgstr "Good job."

msgctxt "408_Sodachi"
msgid "Congratulations, Ehama-san!"
msgstr "¡Felicidades, Ehama-san!"

msgctxt "420_Ehama"
msgid "Thank you so much, everyone. It's all thanks to you. After getting laid off, I was a nobody. But not anymore!"
msgstr "Muchas gracias a todos. Es todo gracias a vosotros. Cuando fui despedido, era un don nadie. ¡Pero eso se acabó!"

msgctxt "432_Sodachi"
msgid "You really looked great out there! And that mask suits you, too. You looked like a hero fighting for justice!"
msgstr "¡Te veías genial ahí fuera! Y esa máscara te queda bien. ¡Parecías un heroe luchando por la justicia!"

msgctxt "444_Ehama"
msgid "Haha. That was definitely the highlight of my life."
msgstr "Jaja. Definitivamente ese fue el punto más alto de mi vida."

msgctxt "456_Ehama"
msgid "I've spent my whole life running. Running from getting hurt, running from fights, running from having to make decisions... Always running."
msgstr "Me he pasado toda la vida huyendo. Huyendo de herirme, huyendo de peleas, huyendo de tomar decisiones... Siempre huyendo."

msgctxt "468_Ehama"
msgid "But I learned something important while training here. It's important to face things head-on without running away, even if it hurts."
msgstr "Pero he aprendido algo importante entrenando aquí. Es importante afrontar las cosas cara a cara y no huir, incluso si duele."

msgctxt "480_Saejima"
msgid "I'll say... You're spot on. Ya really have changed, Ehama. You're a real man now."
msgstr "Diría... Que has dado en el clavo. Has cambiado de verdad, Ehama. Ahora eres un verdadero hombre."

msgctxt "492_Ehama"
msgid "You bet I am. I would've loved to show the new me to my family, too."
msgstr "Puedes apostar que sí. Me habría encantado enseñarle el nuevo yo a mi família también."

msgctxt "504_Ehama"
msgid "They've only seen the bad me over the years."
msgstr "Solo han visto a mi yo malo a lo largo de los años."

msgctxt "516_Sodachi"
msgid "Heheheh. You never know... They may have been watching."
msgstr "Jejeje. Nunca se sabe... Puede que te hayan estado viendo."

msgctxt "528_Ehama"
msgid "Come again?"
msgstr "¿Cómo dices?"

msgctxt "540_Child's Voice"
msgid "Daddy!"
msgstr "¡Papi!"

msgctxt "564_Ehama"
msgid "Koji... Mariko... What are you guys doing here?"
msgstr "Koji... Mariko... ¿Qué estáis haciendo aquí?"

msgctxt "576_Ehama's Wife"
msgid "Sodachi-san was kind enough to tell us where you would be fighting. He asked us to come and watch you."
msgstr "Sodachi-san fue tan amable de decirnos donde estarías luchando. Nos pidió de venir a verte."

msgctxt "588_Ehama's Son"
msgid "You won, daddy! You were so awesome out there! Mommy said that we should all go home together! As a family!"
msgstr "¡Ganaste, papi! ¡Estuviste increíble ahí fuera! ¡Mami dijo que nos iríamos a casa juntos! ¡Como una família!"

msgctxt "600_Ehama"
msgid "Thanks, guys... I can't apologize enough for the way I've acted in the past... *sniffle*"
msgstr "Gracias, chicos... No puedo disculparme lo suficiente por mi forma de actuar en el pasado... *sniff*"

msgctxt "612_Sodachi"
msgid "What a special moment. Truly special."
msgstr "Qué momento tan especial. Verdaderamente especial."

msgctxt "624_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah. And it was real thoughtful of ya to secretly invite his family like that."
msgstr "Sí. Y fue realmente considerado de tu parte invitar en secreto a su família de esa forma."

msgctxt "636_Sodachi"
msgid "Heheheh. It feels like it's the first time I've actually been of any assistance."
msgstr "Jejeje. Siento que es la primera vez que de verdad he sido de ayuda."

msgctxt "648_Saejima"
msgid "Ya got that right. It is the first time."
msgstr "Correcto. Es la primera vez."

msgctxt "660_Sodachi"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "744_Sodachi"
msgid "The dojo's rank has increased."
msgstr "The dojo's rank has increased."

msgctxt "804_Sodachi"
msgid "The dojo's rank increased! Now more apprentices are sure to join, and the money will start flowing! Heheheh!"
msgstr "The dojo's rank increased! Now more apprentices are sure to join, and the money will start flowing! Heheheh!"

msgctxt "816_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "888_Sodachi"
msgid "The dojo's rank decreased! This is a nightmare... Ugh, my chest hurts... The stress is killing me! Saejima-san! Do something!"
msgstr "The dojo's rank decreased! This is a nightmare... Ugh, my chest hurts... The stress is killing me! Saejima-san! Do something!"

msgctxt "900_Saejima"
msgid "(Will he pipe down already...)"
msgstr "(Will he pipe down already...)"

msgctxt "972_Ehama"
msgid "I lost... I knew it. I have no chance of ever becoming a champion."
msgstr "Perdí... Lo sabía. No tengo posibilidades de convertirme nunca en campeón."

msgctxt "984_Sodachi"
msgid "It's too bad about the loss... And it looks like Ehama-san is pretty torn up about the whole thing, too."
msgstr "Es una lástima la derrota... Y parece que Ehama-san está desgarrado por todo el asunto, también."

msgctxt "996_Sodachi"
msgid "But gaining that experience is a big deal. Think of it as a positive outcome and let's keep up the hard training so we can win next time!"
msgstr "Pero ganar esa experiencia es muy importante. ¡Piensa en ello como un resultado positivo y sigamos entrenando duro para que podamos ganar la siguiente ocasión!"

msgctxt "1080_Sodachi"
msgid "Great job! You totally dominated that match! And it appears that Ehama-san has become stronger and more confident because of the fight."
msgstr "¡Buen trabajo! ¡Has dominado totalmente el enfrentamiento! Y parece que Ehama-san se ha hecho más fuerte y seguro en sí mismo por la pelea."

msgctxt "1092_Ehama"
msgid "It was only a short while ago that I got laid off and was totally broke... But now I can earn more than ever just from fighting! What a feeling!"
msgstr "Fue hace poco que fui despedido y estaba totalmente arruinado... ¡Pero ahora puedo ganar mas que nunca solamente de pelear! ¡Qué sensación!"

msgctxt "1104_Sodachi"
msgid "Yes, of course! I will be holding on to that prize money for you, but... Anyway! You won! Keep up the hard work!"
msgstr "Sí, ¡por supuesto! Te guardaré el dinero del premio, pero... ¡De todas formas! ¡Ganaste! ¡Hay que seguir con el trabajo duro!"

msgctxt "1200_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Dragon's Gate. This is a match for beginning fighters. The level of entry isn't high, so it's perfect for practice."
msgstr "Compitiendo en la Puerta del Dragón. Este es un combate para los combatientes principiantes. El nivel de entrada no es alto, así que es perfecto para practicar."

msgctxt "1212_Sodachi"
msgid "This is the beginning of all history. Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "This is the beginning of all history. Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1224_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in a Brawlfest. This is a match for hot-blooded street fighters. I think he should do all right..."
msgstr "Competirás en un Peleatón. Este es un combate para peleadores callejeros aguerridos. Creo que le irá bien..."

msgctxt "1236_Sodachi"
msgid "Fighting connoisseurs! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Fighting connoisseurs! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1248_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Regular Tryouts. This is a match held regularly at the Coliseum for mid-level fighters."
msgstr "You will be competing in the Regular Tryouts. This is a match held regularly at the Coliseum for mid-level fighters."

msgctxt "1260_Sodachi"
msgid "Well, time's a-wasting! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Well, time's a-wasting! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1272_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Shuffle Zone. The skill levels of the fighters in this match are unknown."
msgstr "You will be competing in Shuffle Zone. The skill levels of the fighters in this match are unknown."

msgctxt "1284_Sodachi"
msgid "I hope your opponent isn't too strong... Wow, my heart is racing! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "I hope your opponent isn't too strong... Wow, my heart is racing! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1296_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Big Money match. The prize purse for winning this match is incredible! Money! MONEY! Heheheh!"
msgstr "You will be competing in the Big Money match. The prize purse for winning this match is incredible! Money! MONEY! Heheheh!"

msgctxt "1308_Sodachi"
msgid "All right, let's go! Go Sodachi Dojo! Go get me that money!"
msgstr "All right, let's go! Go Sodachi Dojo! Go get me that money!"

msgctxt "1320_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Rising Stars. This is a famous event where young fighters with great potential gather to prove themselves. A true first step."
msgstr "You will be competing in Rising Stars. This is a famous event where young fighters with great potential gather to prove themselves. A true first step."

msgctxt "1332_Sodachi"
msgid "Well, time's a-wasting! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Well, time's a-wasting! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1344_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Sink or Swim match. This is an event for fighters who are just getting started. Let your skills speak for you."
msgstr "You will be competing in the Sink or Swim match. This is an event for fighters who are just getting started. Let your skills speak for you."

msgctxt "1356_Sodachi"
msgid "Believe in your own abilities! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Believe in your own abilities! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1368_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Winner's Circle. This is an event for undefeated fighters. Be ready for some strong competition."
msgstr "You will be competing in the Winner's Circle. This is an event for undefeated fighters. Be ready for some strong competition."

msgctxt "1380_Sodachi"
msgid "You won't be able to compete again if you lose, so make sure to win! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "You won't be able to compete again if you lose, so make sure to win! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1392_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Veteran's Showdown. This is an event for fighters with a long training history."
msgstr "You will be competing in the Veteran's Showdown. This is an event for fighters with a long training history."

msgctxt "1404_Sodachi"
msgid "It's time to put what you've learned to the test and show 'em who we are! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "It's time to put what you've learned to the test and show 'em who we are! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1416_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Coliseum Opening Fight.\\r\n"\n"It's an extremely high-profile match that is, you guessed it, the opening event at the Coliseum!"
msgstr "You will be competing in the Coliseum Opening Fight.\\r\n"\n"It's an extremely high-profile match that is, you guessed it, the opening event at the Coliseum!"

msgctxt "1428_Sodachi"
msgid "This kind of attention-grabbing fight attracts some pretty strong fighters, but that's no reason for you to lose! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "This kind of attention-grabbing fight attracts some pretty strong fighters, but that's no reason for you to lose! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1440_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in King of the Mountain. This is a very high-level match for skilled fighters who have what it takes to be champion."
msgstr "You will be competing in King of the Mountain. This is a very high-level match for skilled fighters who have what it takes to be champion."

msgctxt "1452_Sodachi"
msgid "Brush up your own skills by fighting stronger opponents. Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Brush up your own skills by fighting stronger opponents. Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1464_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Power Masters."
msgstr "You will be competing in Power Masters."

msgctxt "1476_Sodachi"
msgid "Fighters proud of their power gather at this event, so the fights are sure to be intense. Give it your all, super Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Fighters proud of their power gather at this event, so the fights are sure to be intense. Give it your all, super Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1488_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Speed Masters."
msgstr "You will be competing in Speed Masters."

msgctxt "1500_Sodachi"
msgid "Fighters proud of their level of speed gather at this event. You're perfect for this one! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Fighters proud of their level of speed gather at this event. You're perfect for this one! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1512_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Technique Masters."
msgstr "You will be competing in Technique Masters."

msgctxt "1524_Sodachi"
msgid "Only fighters with superior technique fight in this event, so stay focused! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Only fighters with superior technique fight in this event, so stay focused! Go Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "1536_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Rookie Stars. As the name suggests, this is a match for rookie fighters aiming to be number one."
msgstr "You will be competing in Rookie Stars. As the name suggests, this is a match for rookie fighters aiming to be number one."

msgctxt "1548_Sodachi"
msgid "This is the highest level match, so make sure you're ready. Go Sodachi Dojo, the strongest dojo in Kamurocho!"
msgstr "This is the highest level match, so make sure you're ready. Go Sodachi Dojo, the strongest dojo in Kamurocho!"

msgctxt "1572_Ehama"
msgid "I lost... I knew it. I have no chance of ever becoming a champion."
msgstr "Perdí... Lo sabía. No tengo posibilidades de convertirme nunca en campeón."

msgctxt "1584_Sodachi"
msgid "It's too bad about the loss... And it looks like Ehama-san is pretty torn up about the whole thing, too."
msgstr "Es una lástima la derrota... Y parece que Ehama-san está desgarrado por todo el asunto, también."

msgctxt "1596_Sodachi"
msgid "But gaining that experience is a big deal. Think of it as a positive outcome and let's keep up the hard training so we can win next time!"
msgstr "Pero ganar esa experiencia es muy importante. ¡Piensa en ello como un resultado positivo y sigamos entrenando duro para que podamos ganar la siguiente ocasión!"

msgctxt "1692_Sodachi"
msgid "It's time to participate in a tournament. Don't worry Ehama-san, you've worked really hard. You can win this."
msgstr "Es hora de participar en un torneo. No te preocupes Ehama-san, has trabajado realmente duro. Puedes ganar esto."

msgctxt "1704_Saejima"
msgid "That's right. Doesn't matter whether ya win or lose. Just give it everythin' ya got."
msgstr "Eso es. No importa si ganas o pierdes. Solamente da todo lo que tengas."

msgctxt "1716_Ehama"
msgid "Right! I'm going to show everyone the new person I've become!"
msgstr "¡De acuerdo! ¡Voy a enseñar a todo el mundo la nueva persona en la que me he convertido!"

msgctxt "1728_Sodachi"
msgid "Snag that champion belt and you won't have to worry about the sadness of being laid off ever again! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "¡Agarra ese cinturón de campeón y no tendrás que preocuparte por la tristeza de que te despidan nunca más! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1764_Sodachi"
msgid "Wow, you really are an amazing fighter! I'm sure your apprentice learned a lot, too."
msgstr "Wow, ¡realmente eres un luchador increíble! Estoy seguro de que tu aprendiz también aprendió mucho."

msgctxt "1776_Ehama"
msgid "I lost... You're really strong. I guess I just have to work even harder."
msgstr "He perdido... Eres realmente fuerte. Supongo que tengo que trabajar más duro todavía."

msgctxt "1788_Saejima"
msgid "(Looks like he learned a lot...)"
msgstr "(Parece que ha aprendido mucho...)"

msgctxt "1884_Sodachi"
msgid "Sparring or not, I can't believe you lost! Looks like Ehama-san is getting a lot better!"
msgstr "Entrenamiento o no, ¡no puedo creer que hayas perdido! ¡Parece que Ehama-san está mejorando mucho!"

msgctxt "1896_Ehama"
msgid "Saejima-san... I wanted you to fight with everything you've got. You were just taking it easy on me, weren't you?"
msgstr "Saejima-san... Quería que lucharas con todas tus fuerzas. Estabas poniéndomelo fácil, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "1908_Sodachi"
msgid "Er... It was good practice, but it looks like he's lost some trust in you..."
msgstr "Em... Ha sido una buena práctica, pero parece que ha perdido algo de confianza en tí..."

msgctxt "1992_Sodachi"
msgid "It's time for some sparring. Saejima-san, face Ehama-san one-on-one so that you can see just how much he's grown."
msgstr "Es hora de entrenar. Saejima-san, enfrentate a Ehama-san en un uno contra uno para que veas cuánto ha mejorado."

msgctxt "2004_Saejima"
msgid "All right. I'm eager to find out how much ya can do. And don't hold back. Gimme everythin' ya got."
msgstr "Muy bien. Estoy ansioso de descubrir cuánto puedes hacer. Y no te contengas. Dame todo lo que tengas."

msgctxt "2016_Ehama"
msgid "Right! I'll give it everything I've got!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Lo daré todo!"

msgctxt "2040_Sodachi"
msgid "I see you've selected solo training. It's important to test his level of independence."
msgstr "Veo que has elegido el entrenamiento en solitario. Es importante poner a prueba su independencia."

msgctxt "2052_Saejima"
msgid "All right. You can choose yer own trainin' routine. Just don't go slackin' off."
msgstr "All right. You can choose yer own trainin' routine. Just don't go slackin' off."

msgctxt "2064_Ehama"
msgid "Okay! Leave it to me!"
msgstr "¡Vale! ¡Déjamelo a mí!"

msgctxt "2124_Saejima"
msgid "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"
msgstr "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"

msgctxt "2136_Ehama"
msgid "I learned a lot, even though it was just me!"
msgstr "He aprendido mucho, ¡y eso que solo era yo!"

msgctxt "2148_Ehama"
msgid "I would have never lost my job if I'd been able to behave this independently at work! Haha!"
msgstr "¡Nunca habría perdido mi trabajo y hubiera sido capaz de ser tan independiente en el trabajo! ¡Jaja!"

msgctxt "2160_Saejima"
msgid "(Huh. Not bad.)"
msgstr "(Heh. No está mal.)"

msgctxt "2196_Saejima"
msgid "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"
msgstr "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"

msgctxt "2208_Ehama"
msgid "Okay, I guess... It's always been hard for me to stay focused when I'm on my own."
msgstr "Vale, Supongo... que siempre ha sido difícil para mí el estar concentrado cuando estoy yo solo."

msgctxt "2220_Saejima"
msgid "(Not too bad. I guess...)"
msgstr "(Not too bad. I guess...)"

msgctxt "2256_Saejima"
msgid "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"
msgstr "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"

msgctxt "2268_Ehama"
msgid "Honestly, it didn't go very well at all."
msgstr "La verdad. No ha ido para nada bien."

msgctxt "2280_Ehama"
msgid "No wonder my family is so disgusted with me. Ha... haha..."
msgstr "No me extraña que mi família esté tan disgustada conmigo. Ja... jaja..."

msgctxt "2292_Saejima"
msgid "(Hm... That didn't go so well.)"
msgstr "(Mm... No salió muy bien)."

msgctxt "2376_Saejima"
msgid "How's about we rest this time? Rest is important too."
msgstr "How's about we rest this time? Rest is important too."

msgctxt "2388_Sodachi"
msgid "Yay! That's a wonderful idea! Let's rest away!"
msgstr "Yay! That's a wonderful idea! Let's rest away!"

msgctxt "2472_Ehama"
msgid "Zzz..."
msgstr "Zzz..."

msgctxt "2484_Sodachi"
msgid "Zzz... Gaaaa... Gaaaa... Mmmm..."
msgstr "Zzz... Gaaaa... Gaaaa... Mmmm..."

msgctxt "2520_Sodachi"
msgid "Googa googa... Nyaar... Zzz...\\r\n"\n"Heheh, but I can't eat anymore... Zzz..."
msgstr "Googa googa... Nyaar... Zzz...\\r\n"\n"Jeje, pero no puedo comer más... Zzz..."

msgctxt "2532_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "2604_Sodachi"
msgid "Wow! I feel so refreshed! Resting really is necessary sometimes."
msgstr "Wow! I feel so refreshed! Resting really is necessary sometimes."

msgctxt "2688_Saejima"
msgid "All right. This time I'm gonna teach ya a potential Finishing Move."
msgstr "All right. This time I'm gonna teach ya a potential Finishing Move."

msgctxt "2700_Saejima"
msgid "(Which move should I teach 'im?)"
msgstr "(Which move should I teach 'im?)"

msgctxt "2736_Saejima"
msgid "Okay, let's get started."
msgstr "Okay, let's get started."

msgctxt "2748_Saejima"
msgid "Let's work on the move you ain't mastered yet. Okay, let's get started."
msgstr "Vamos a enfocarnos en el movimiento que aún no has dominado. Bien, empecemos."

msgctxt "2820_Saejima"
msgid "...So, that's it. Think ya got it?"
msgstr "...So, that's it. Think ya got it?"

msgctxt "2832_Ehama"
msgid "Honestly, I didn't really understand it. I think I'm too old. I've lost too many brain cells..."
msgstr "La verdad, no lo entiendo. Creo que soy muy viejo. He perdido muchas neuronas..."

msgctxt "2844_Saejima"
msgid "(He couldn't learn it after one try, but he'll get it next time.)"
msgstr "(No ha podido aprenderlo en un intento, pero lo conseguirá la próxima vez.)"

msgctxt "2928_Saejima"
msgid "I'm sure ya got it down now. Give it a try."
msgstr "I'm sure ya got it down now. Give it a try."

msgctxt "2940_Sodachi"
msgid "Go easy on me, please."
msgstr "Go easy on me, please."

msgctxt "2952_Sodachi"
msgid "Aaaaagh!"
msgstr "¡Aaaaagh!"

msgctxt "2976_Saejima"
msgid "Good! You did it just right that time. Now don't forget what ya learned."
msgstr "Good! You did it just right that time. Now don't forget what ya learned."

msgctxt "3000_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Slam<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Slam<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3012_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Suplex SP<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Suplex SP<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3024_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Throw<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Throw<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3036_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Flying Knee<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Flying Knee<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3048_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Smashing<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Smashing<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3060_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Face Crushing<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Face Crushing<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3072_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Clotheslining<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Clotheslining<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3084_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Fence Smashing<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Fence Smashing<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3096_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Might<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Might<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3108_Sodachi"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Crush<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Crush<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3192_Sodachi"
msgid "Welcome back. Did you guys have a good time? You know, next time you can take me along, too. If you want that is..."
msgstr "Bienvenido de nuevo. ¿Habéis pasado un buen rato? Sabes, la próxima vez podrías llevarme con vosotros. Si queréis, claro..."

msgctxt "3216_Sodachi"
msgid "All right, see you next time."
msgstr "All right, see you next time."

msgctxt "3276_Saejima"
msgid "How's about we call it quits for today n' go out for a drink?"
msgstr "How's about we call it quits for today n' go out for a drink?"

msgctxt "3288_Sodachi"
msgid "That sounds great! You have to know how to separate work and play, right? Wait..."
msgstr "That sounds great! You have to know how to separate work and play, right? Wait..."

msgctxt "3300_Saejima"
msgid "See ya later."
msgstr "Nos vemos."

msgctxt "3312_Sodachi"
msgid "Okay! Have a good time! Be back by dinnertime!"
msgstr "¡Vale! ¡Pasadlo bien! ¡Volved para la cena!"

msgctxt "3324_Sodachi"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "3396_Sodachi"
msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr "Mmmm..."

msgctxt "3408_Saejima"
msgid "Somethin' wrong?"
msgstr "Somethin' wrong?"

msgctxt "3420_Sodachi"
msgid "Nothing... It's just that lately Ehama-san seems down for some reason..."
msgstr "Nada... Es solo que últimamente Ehama-san parece desanimada por alguna razón..."

msgctxt "3432_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "3444_Sodachi"
msgid "We've been pushing him in training for a long time now, so if he doesn't win a tournament soon he may just give up on us..."
msgstr "We've been pushing him in training for a long time now, so if he doesn't win a tournament soon he may just give up on us..."

msgctxt "3516_Sodachi"
msgid "Ehama-san lost..."
msgstr "Ehama-san ha perdido..."

msgctxt "3528_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah... Where is he right now?"
msgstr "Yeah... Where is he right now?"

msgctxt "3540_Sodachi"
msgid "Now that you mention it, he hasn't come back to the dojo at all. I guess the loss was a shock."
msgstr "Now that you mention it, he hasn't come back to the dojo at all. I guess the loss was a shock."

msgctxt "3552_Sodachi"
msgid "I'll go and look for him!"
msgstr "I'll go and look for him!"

msgctxt "3564_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "3624_Sodachi"
msgid "*pant* Here he is!"
msgstr "*jadeo* ¡Aquí está!"

msgctxt "3636_Ehama"
msgid "I'm sorry... I made you all worry..."
msgstr "Lo siento... Hice que se preocuparan..."

msgctxt "3648_Sodachi"
msgid "You had us worried sick!"
msgstr "¡Nos tenías muy preocupados!"

msgctxt "3660_Ehama"
msgid "I just can't believe that I couldn't win, even after everything that you guys taught me."
msgstr "I just can't believe that I couldn't win, even after everything that you guys taught me."

msgctxt "3672_Ehama"
msgid "I guess I'm just not good enough. I don't think I'll ever change."
msgstr "I guess I'm just not good enough. I don't think I'll ever change."

msgctxt "3684_Sodachi"
msgid "That's not true, Ehama-san. But if you quit now, everything will have been for nothing. How about giving it just one more try, huh?"
msgstr "That's not true, Ehama-san. But if you quit now, everything will have been for nothing. How about giving it just one more try, huh?"

msgctxt "3696_Ehama"
msgid "I guess... Trying can't hurt... Besides, I don't have anything else to do anyway."
msgstr "I guess... Trying can't hurt... Besides, I don't have anything else to do anyway."

msgctxt "3708_Saejima"
msgid "(I'm glad he's back, but it looks like he's lost a lot o' motivation. Better get him that champion belt. And quick...)"
msgstr "(Me alegra que haya vuelto, pero parece que ha perdido mucha motivación. Será mejor conseguirle ese cinturón de campeón. Y rápido...)."

msgctxt "3792_Sodachi"
msgid "Hey, Saejima-san! I was waiting for you! Shall we start our training now?"
msgstr "Hey, Saejima-san! I was waiting for you! Shall we start our training now?"

msgctxt "3804_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, let's get started."
msgstr "Yeah, let's get started."

msgctxt "3816_Sodachi"
msgid "All right! Here's to another day of training! Let's get to work!"
msgstr "All right! Here's to another day of training! Let's get to work!"

msgctxt "3840_Saejima"
msgid "Maybe later."
msgstr "Maybe later."

msgctxt "3852_Sodachi"
msgid "Oh, that's too bad. But you are a pretty busy person. Come back when you have more time."
msgstr "Oh, that's too bad. But you are a pretty busy person. Come back when you have more time."

msgctxt "3864_Sodachi"
msgid "Start Training"
msgstr "Start Training"

msgctxt "3876_Sodachi"
msgid "Not Now"
msgstr "Ahora no"

